title: Purpose of the Data Governance Team
text: The data governance team provides oversight to the data quality process.

title: Escalating Resolution
text: The data governance team defines and enforces data governance policies and standards, which include data quality.

title: Purpose of the Data Quality Team
text: The data quality team monitors data quality dashboards to hold parties accountable for remediating data quality issues, and is not the same role as the data governance team.
